
NAME 
     temp-script
     
DESCRIPTION
     create & execute a temporary shell script
       ~ optionally define 'histfile' to write to bash history
       ~ optionally define 'my_tmp_dir' to specify custom temp directory
       
SYNOPSIS
     temp-script [options]...
     
EXAMPLES
     temp-script 
     temp-script --new
     temp-script --last
     
AVAILABLE OPTIONS:
     --new        -- create a new temporary script
     --last       -- re-run the last temporary script
     